# Header

A site header component with slots for logo and navigation.

## Import

```typescript
import { Header } from '@happyvertical/svelte';
```

## Basic Usage

<div class="example">
  <div class="example-preview" style="width: 100%;">
    <Header>
      {#snippet logo()}
        <h1>Town News</h1>
      {/snippet}
      {#snippet nav()}
        <a href="#">Home</a>
        <a href="#">Articles</a>
        <a href="#">About</a>
      {/snippet}
    </Header>
  </div>
</div>

```svelte
<Header>
  {#snippet logo()}
    <h1>Town News</h1>
  {/snippet}
  {#snippet nav()}
    <a href="/">Home</a>
    <a href="/articles">Articles</a>
    <a href="/about">About</a>
  {/snippet}
</Header>
```

