## Features

- **Primary background**: Uses `--color-primary-main` for brand consistency
- **Inverse text**: White text on colored background
- **Responsive layout**: Stacks vertically on mobile, horizontal on desktop
- **Built-in Container**: Content is automatically contained
- **Link styling**: Navigation links have hover effects

## Responsive Behavior

- **Mobile**: Logo and nav stack vertically
- **Desktop (768px+)**: Logo and nav side-by-side

## Props

| Prop | Type | Default | Description |
|------|------|---------|-------------|
| `logo` | `Snippet` | - | Logo/site title content |
| `nav` | `Snippet` | - | Navigation links |

## Styling Notes

The header automatically styles elements inside the snippets:

```svelte
<!-- h1 in logo slot: large, semibold, no margin -->
{#snippet logo()}
  <h1>Site Name</h1>
{/snippet}

<!-- Links in nav slot: white, medium weight, hover underline -->
{#snippet nav()}
  <a href="/">Link</a>
{/snippet}
```
